  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Enforcement Rules have been incorporated pursuant to Article 46 of Fire Services Act (the Act).]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fire regulating authorities referred in Article 3 of the Act shall refer to National Fire Administration if the transactions fall within the scope of MOI; or FireDepartment, within municipal, or county/city government.
County/city police department shall undertake the transactions before the establishment of a fire department by the county/city government.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Municipal, county/city government shall develop an annual plan to undertake fire education and propaganda from time to time.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
